  "content_summary": "Official reference implementation for TOON, a compact JSON-compatible serialization format optimized for LLM token budgets. Combines YAML indentation with CSV-style tabular rows for uniform arrays. Claims ~40% token reduction vs JSON with comparable or better accuracy across 5016 LLM calls. Best for tabular data; minified JSON can beat TOON when structure is deeply nested."
